text: Henny Moan (22 February 1936 — 8 September 2024) was a Norwegian actress. She was known for her roles in the Oscar-nominated movie Nine Lives (1957) and Lake of the Dead (1958). Moan was born in Talvik, Finnmark. She grew up in counties Gratangen and Narvik.https://nbl.snl.no/Henny_Moan. Norsk biografisk leksikon. Retrieved 2024-09-10 Moan was married to the author André Bjerke from 1959 until 1972. She was also in a relationship with musician Ole Paus from 1973 to 1976. Moan died on 8 September 2024 at the age of 88. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1936 births Category:2024 deaths Category:Norwegian movie actors Category:Norwegian stage actors Category:Norwegian television actors
